answer:
The need for Tetanus-diphtheria (Td) vaccine or Tetanus Immune Globulin (TIg) after an injury is determined by a healthcare provider. The healthcare provider will assess the type of wound and your immunization history to determine your plan of care. If Td is needed, you don't need to wait before getting the vaccine. Speak with your healthcare provider. 
Immunization Nurse
